[
  {
    "startTime": 9.22,
    "endTime": 12.069,
    "text": "Hello, and welcome to today’s Grammar Gameshow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.34,
    "endTime": 13.861,
    "text": "I’m your host, Will!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.9,
    "endTime": 16.616,
    "text": "But, I’m no instant decision!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.244,
    "endTime": 22.719,
    "text": "And of course let’s not forget Leslie, our all-knowing voice in the sky."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.75,
    "endTime": 23.937,
    "text": "Hello everyone!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 24.0,
    "endTime": 27.694,
    "text": "Tonight we’re going to ask you three questions about..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.7,
    "endTime": 29.669999999999998,
    "text": "Adverbs of frequency!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.7,
    "endTime": 36.69,
    "text": "Yes, those short words like \"always\" and \"sometimes\" that tell us how often people do things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.8,
    "endTime": 39.660999999999994,
    "text": "OK! Now, let’s meet our contestants!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.8,
    "endTime": 41.421,
    "text": "Hi, everyone. I’m Mike!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.6,
    "endTime": 43.186,
    "text": "Contestant number 2?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.2,
    "endTime": 45.447,
    "text": "Hi, Will. My name’s Sarah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.5,
    "endTime": 47.293,
    "text": "Welcome back, Sarah!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.4,
    "endTime": 52.567,
    "text": "OK! Let’s get going and don’t forget you can play along at home, too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.107,
    "endTime": 56.092,
    "text": "Our first question is a sorting question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 56.2,
    "endTime": 62.635000000000005,
    "text": "Listen to these sentences and put them in the correct order from most often to least often."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.7,
    "endTime": 63.835,
    "text": "Here we go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 63.9,
    "endTime": 67.712,
    "text": "a) I always ride my bike to school."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 67.8,
    "endTime": 71.271,
    "text": "b) He never sleeps before nine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.3,
    "endTime": 75.494,
    "text": "c) She sometimes misses breakfast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.6,
    "endTime": 79.46499999999999,
    "text": "d) You often go on holiday."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.6,
    "endTime": 82.847,
    "text": "e) It rarely rains here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.095,
    "endTime": 91.134,
    "text": "A, D, C, E, B."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 91.3,
    "endTime": 94.823,
    "text": "Always, often, sometimes, rarely, never."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.9,
    "endTime": 95.733,
    "text": "Leslie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.9,
    "endTime": 96.96600000000001,
    "text": "Well done!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.0,
    "endTime": 100.309,
    "text": "As you said, from most often to least often:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.5,
    "endTime": 102.146,
    "text": "I \"always\" ride..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.3,
    "endTime": 103.994,
    "text": "You \"often\" go..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.1,
    "endTime": 106.231,
    "text": "She \"sometimes\" misses..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.25,
    "endTime": 107.751,
    "text": "It \"rarely\" rains..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.8,
    "endTime": 109.40599999999999,
    "text": "He \"never\" sleeps..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.5,
    "endTime": 110.795,
    "text": "Good job, Mike."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.8,
    "endTime": 118.071,
    "text": "You know sometimes a contestant will come along and really dazzle me with their intelligence and knowledge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.532,
    "endTime": 119.904,
    "text": "Not today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 121.136,
    "text": "One point for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.36,
    "endTime": 123.33,
    "text": "Question two."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.5,
    "endTime": 130.873,
    "text": "What must you remember about the form of the main verb when using adverbs \"never\" and \"rarely\"?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.326,
    "endTime": 136.215,
    "text": "The verb must be positive not negative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.3,
    "endTime": 137.50300000000001,
    "text": "Leslie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.51,
    "endTime": 138.637,
    "text": "Superb!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.7,
    "endTime": 142.594,
    "text": "\"Never\" and \"rarely\" must take a positive verb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.6,
    "endTime": 145.493,
    "text": "I never study. I rarely go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.5,
    "endTime": 149.46,
    "text": "Good job Mike. Have 16 and a half points."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.6,
    "endTime": 153.678,
    "text": "You don’t never need to worry with an answer like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.678,
    "endTime": 154.345,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.4,
    "endTime": 155.50300000000001,
    "text": "Wait, what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.6,
    "endTime": 157.629,
    "text": "Now for our final question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.75,
    "endTime": 163.136,
    "text": "Look at this sentence and tell me where the adverb \"frequency\" should go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.04,
    "endTime": 168.67,
    "text": "Position B! Just before the main verb!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.7,
    "endTime": 169.676,
    "text": "Leslie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.8,
    "endTime": 172.27300000000002,
    "text": "Yes, Sarah. That’s right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.3,
    "endTime": 176.49300000000002,
    "text": "Good job, Sarah ! You aren’t asleep after all."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.5,
    "endTime": 183.318,
    "text": "You can have five points, or you can gamble and go for 150 points."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.318,
    "endTime": 184.502,
    "text": "What would you like to do?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.957,
    "endTime": 190.676,
    "text": "Gamble?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.8,
    "endTime": 194.90800000000002,
    "text": "Everyone loves an entertaining fool!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.1,
    "endTime": 196.47799999999998,
    "text": "Here’s your question."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.6,
    "endTime": 201.85999999999999,
    "text": "Look at this sentence and tell me where the adverb of \"frequency\" should go?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.892,
    "endTime": 207.279,
    "text": "Nice try!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.3,
    "endTime": 208.871,
    "text": "It’s position B again!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.9,
    "endTime": 210.035,
    "text": "Leslie?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.2,
    "endTime": 211.803,
    "text": "Wrong, I’m afraid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.9,
    "endTime": 213.761,
    "text": "You were right in the first case."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.8,
    "endTime": 217.61700000000002,
    "text": "The adverb of frequency goes before the main verb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.65,
    "endTime": 223.235,
    "text": "Unless, like in the second case, the main verb is the verb be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.3,
    "endTime": 227.091,
    "text": "Then, the adverb of frequency goes after."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.2,
    "endTime": 230.357,
    "text": "I’m sorry Sarah. That was wrong!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 230.5,
    "endTime": 232.37,
    "text": "Minus 12 points."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 232.5,
    "endTime": 235.845,
    "text": "Well, that brings us to the end of today’s Grammar Gameshow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.0,
    "endTime": 237.721,
    "text": "Let’s count out the points."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.8,
    "endTime": 239.29700000000003,
    "text": "And the winner is..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.4,
    "endTime": 242.3,
    "text": "Mike! With 412."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.193,
    "endTime": 248.804,
    "text": "Well done! Here’s what you’ve won!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 251.134,
    "text": "It’s a pen!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 251.659,
    "endTime": 254.749,
    "text": "You can finally practice your spelling!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.9,
    "endTime": 256.862,
    "text": "And how did you do at home?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.9,
    "endTime": 261.50199999999995,
    "text": "We’ll see you again next week, where you can play for an even bigger prize."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 261.7,
    "endTime": 262.844,
    "text": "And Sarah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.9,
    "endTime": 265.902,
    "text": "You barely got in the game at all!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.0,
    "endTime": 267.189,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.3,
    "endTime": 269.482,
    "text": "I think it’s because..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.528,
    "endTime": 271.879,
    "text": "Fascinating!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.0,
    "endTime": 273.942,
    "text": "Feed her to the sharks!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.0,
    "endTime": 277.507,
    "text": "It looks like we’ll need another contestant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 277.6,
    "endTime": 278.86,
    "text": "Thanks for joining us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.9,
    "endTime": 280.44199999999995,
    "text": "Say goodbye, Leslie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.5,
    "endTime": 282.023,
    "text": "Goodbye, Leslie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.717,
    "endTime": 286.018,
    "text": "See you next time!"
  }
]